creator: App Takeoff
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to NTA!

For the first time ever, you can effortlessly stay connected to your team, access and share media, and find resources within seconds!

The recruiting process is now easier than ever before. You can share specific media to fit a person's needs and get them going in no time!

Welcome to the team!
